Enum File

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<File>
com.github.bhlangonijr.chesslib.File
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<File>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum File extends Enum<File>
The files in a board. A file is a column in the chessboard, and it is identified as a letter from A to H.

Each value defines a single file, except for the special value NONE which represents no file.
